        <Parent_String>gilding for bookbinding processes and techniques [300263342], bookbinding processes and techniques [300234780], bookbinding and bookbinding processes and techniques [300234771], object-making processes and techniques [300053588], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
